      • ParseLocaleDate

        public ParseLocaleDate(String pattern,
               boolean lenient,
               Locale locale,
               TimeZone timeZone,
               DateCellProcessor next)
        パラメータ:
        pattern - the date format pattern (required).
        lenient - whether date interpretation is lenient.
        locale - the date format locale. if locale is null, use default value with Locale.getDefault() (optional).
        timeZone - the date format timeZone (optional).
        next - the next processor in the chain (required).
        例外:
        IllegalArgumentException - if pattern is null or empty.
